    Represents additional metadata fields that may be present in external metadata files or additional manifest files across various eLearning standards (e.g., SCORM 2004, AICC).

    Represents metadata for a SCORM 2004 eLearning module, including SCORM 2004-specific fields such as sequencing information, mastery score, custom data, prerequisites, and additional metadata from external manifests.

    Builder for constructing instances of Scorm2004Metadata.

    Represents generic sequencing information for eLearning modules, encapsulating rules, navigation flow, and objectives to support multiple eLearning standards (SCORM, xAPI, AICC, etc.).

    Builder class for constructing instances of SequencingInfo.
